body:
changing the code above to
```
    sess.run(update_op)
    res += [sess.run([x, y])]
```
does indeed result in 
```
1.2.0
100.0
10.0
```
as expected. Is this intended behaviour? (the execution order of the list of ops changing randomly with each call)
